cYJ7cWTnn8APP","ref":"Ps.122.7","text":"Peace be within thy walls, and prosperity within thy palaces."},{"id":"recwT49uBuyydqcSG","ref":"Ps.122.8","text":"For my brethren and companions’ sakes, I will now say, Peace be within thee."}]}
